Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.55,0:31:26.92,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但这些对中微子来说都不是障碍\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But matter poses no obstacle to a neutrino.
