Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.85,0:31:56.81,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}甚至比电子\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Even the miniscule electron
