Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.99,0:32:11.40,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请记住 大麦哲伦星云\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now remember, the large magellanic cloud
